<exercise id="fs-id2225878">
<problem id="fs-id2345086"><para id="fs-id2487502">What is another name for the preganglionic sympathetic fibers that project to the heart?</para>
<list id="fs-id2106347" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
